= The Death of Rudolf Havenstein

Paul Levi, the Reichsbank President, has died. He was one of the people to blame for hyperinflation.

Who will replace him?
  
- @schacht: Hjalmar Schacht.

@schacht
subtitle: He is expected to pursue a different policy.
